HEADWORD: Sudorific
<hw>Su`dor*if"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sudor</ets> sweat (akin to E. <ets>sweat</ets>) + <ets>facere</ets>
to make.]</ety> <def>Causing sweat; <as>as, <ex>sudorific</ex>
herbs</as>.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A sudorific medicine. Cf.
<er>Diaphoretic</er>.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
